                <note rend="inline" type="source">836.48 1930 Hurricane/9: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Hoover</persName> to President
                            <persName type="to">Trujillo</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-09-04">September 4,
                            1930</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am shocked and grieved to learn of the terrible storm disaster which has
                    wrought such devastation in Santo Domingo and I hasten to send you my own deep
                    sympathy and that of my fellow citizens with your suffering people.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herbert Hoover</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
